'''''Polyhedron'' 90''' was a roleplaying magazine published in [[December]] [[1993]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''. The article was called ''[[The New Republic Campaign: The Battle for Endor from the PCs' Perspective]]'' and was written by [[Bill Slavicsek]].

Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

